  -files/eselect-compiler-2.0.0_beta2-specs.patch,
  -eselect-compiler-2.0.0_beta2-r2.ebuild,
  +eselect-compiler-2.0.0_beta3.ebuild:
  Some more cross compilation fixes.

*eselect-compiler-2.0.0_beta2-r2 (05 Oct 2005)

